These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, pall-mall, tiparillo
1. the person watching adventure movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Cigar     | pall-mall    | tiparillo       | fonseca |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, vegafina, havana
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Cigar   | fonseca  | vegafina  | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, water, soy-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, r&b, techno
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking water is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | water | cola |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | techno    | r&b        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, spriteing, video-games
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, iced-tea
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is spriteing##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is spriteing##3
3. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | spriteing | baking |
| Beverage     | cola  | sprite    | iced-tea  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, montecristo
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is between the game-smoker and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | game | old-henry | montecristo |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
House: colonial, palace, farmhouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the colonial house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
4. the colonial house is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| House   | farmhouse | colonial | palace      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

