.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, corn, spinach
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, dutch, malaysian
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | corn  | spinach    | kale       |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person drinking cola is the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk        | fanta  | cola   |
| Game       | monopoly | scrabble | whist |

