.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, turquise, purple
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
2. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | water      |
| Color   | turquise       | fuchsia | purple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
