.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf | tennis |

