.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, malaysian
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, canasta
1. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing canasta is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing billiard##2
4. the person playing billiard is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | american | malaysian | colombian |
| Game           | backgammon    | canasta    | billiard       |

