.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, snowboarding, swimming
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Pet   | snake    | chinchilla   | goldfish |
| Sport   | snowboarding | swimming | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-15::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, teacher
City: colone, london, edinburgh
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the bartender is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Job           | doctor | teacher | bartender |
| City   | london  | edinburgh    | colone     |

