.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, indie, trance
1. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the fan of trance and the fan of ambient##2
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of trance is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | october | february | august |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | indie  | trance    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, badminton
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Sport       | badminton    | rugby | swimming  |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van        | scooter |

