.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman, dunhill
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Cigar      | dunhill    | chaman | dannemann         |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts  | documentary |

 